Deborah Maria Luisa Moore (amụrụ na 27 Ọktoba 1963) bụ ọnye England na-eme ihe nkírí
Ọ bụ nwa nwanyị nke onye na-eme ihe nkírí Roger Moore na ónyé na-ese ihe nkírí Itali Luisa Mattioli.

O mèrè nke mbụ ya na TV dị ka nwatakịrị na The Persuaders! ihe omume "The Long Goodbye" nke nnà ya na Tony Curtis na-eme ihe nkiri, na mbido ọrụ ya, a na-akpọkarị ya "Deborah Barrymore". Ọ pụtara na ihe nkírí ndị dị ka Lionheart (1987), Alien Terminator (1988), 1990 comedy, Bullseye! (n'ihu nna ya), Chaplin (1992), Into the Sun (1992), na South Kensington (2001). O yikarịrị ka a maara ya nke ọma na UK dị ka ihu nke mkpọsa mgbasa ozi Scottish Widows site na 1986 ruo 1995 mgbè Amanda Lamb nọchiri ya
O mechara were aha Deborah Moore.
Ọ pụtara ugboro abụọ na mmepụta James Bond

Ọ rụrụ ọrụ odeakwụkwọ na 1989 biopic Goldeneye: The Secret Life of Ian Fleming ma mesịa pụta dị ka ónyé na-elekọta ụgbọ elu na 2002 Bond film, Die Another Day, nke bụ ihe nkírí Bond nke anọ na nke ikpeazụ nke Pierce Brosnan. Ọ pụtakwara na ihe nkiri TV nke 1998 Merlin: The Quest Begins, n'ihu Jason Connery, nwa nke onye bụbu Bond Sean Connery. Nna nna ya bụ ónyé na-eme ihe nkiri Robert Brown, ónyé nna ya na-eme na usoro telivishọn Ivanhoe na ihe nkírí Bond atọ.
